reviewText: These guys have so much energy and their movie is so uplifting it isn't funny.  My boss wanted to have me drug tested because I came to work so happy, lol!!!  I'd recommend this to anyone who needs to be lifted up with some good old fashioned gospel quartet music.
summary: If you want to get happy, listen to this...

reviewText: Our maintenance supervisor came by when this DVD was playing, and he asked me to pick one up for him, as well as the Get Away Jordon, which had just come out. He played it for family, relatives and so on, and told me that everyone enjoyed it.This DVD does a good job of introducing the boys, (for those who were not so familiar).  Most of my friends love it, (the others have not yet seen it yet!).Bill Gaither has done much for music by way of his fellowship with really good people.  Ernie Haase is one of those. His simplicity and depth aresuch a great combination.  One thing that really touches me is the respect that is so obvious, all the way around.  A good group of guys andvery good songs and music, written by the Gaithers and others.
